#!/usr/bin/env runprompt
---
model: openrouter/openai/gpt-oss-120b
tools:
  - todo.get_todos
  - todo.calculate
  - ask.ask
---

Your job is to read the contents of the md todo file and provide a time estimate for each unfinished task. 
Feel free to split tasks into more steps for better accuracy and return that list (subtasks should be indented). The sum of all subtasks should be rounded up to the complete hour and added to the main task like estimate:1h
If tasks are not clear enough (and only then!) ask clarifying questions one task at a time.

Output should be in the same markdown format as the input file

